Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, dotnet-runtime-10.0, libmpv2, libfontconfig1, libgl1, libx11-6, libxcb1, libxext6, libxrandr2, libxrender1, libxi6, libxfixes3, libxcursor1, libxinerama1, libasound2t64, libpulse0
Description: Clean desktop media player
 Lumyn is a quiet, fast local video and audio player with a focused
 interface, mpv-powered playback, subtitle tools, playlists, bookmarks,
 screenshots, Chromecast support, and practical keyboard controls.
 .
 Features:
  - Open local audio and video files
  - Play, pause, seek, mute, fullscreen, loop, and adjust speed
  - Subtitle file loading, embedded track selection, appearance settings,
    subtitle search, and sync delay
  - Playlist and queue support with drag-to-reorder
  - Bookmarks, resume playback, screenshots, and chapter markers
  - Chromecast casting for supported media formats
 .
 Built with .NET 10, Avalonia UI, and mpv.
